{"tid":1563862,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"眾說 QC仔唱「香港國歌」年輕化","createTime":"2019-09-12T14:24:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T14:28:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"248ee51ed9633680d440c73790b5d3fe1fbbfc2e","tid":1563862,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:24:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/23468/%E4%BA%BA%E9%8F%88-%E9%A1%98%E6%A6%AE%E5%85%89%E6%AD%B8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E7%9A%87%E4%BB%81%E6%9B%B8%E9%99%A2-23468/qc%E4%BB%94%E5%94%B1%E3%80%8C%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%8C%E3%80%8D%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E5%8C%96\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F23468%2F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%258F%2588-%25E9%25A1%2598%25E6%25A6%25AE%25E5%2585%2589%25E6%25AD%25B8%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E7%259A%2587%25E4%25BB%2581%25E6%259B%25B8%25E9%2599%25A2-23468%2Fqc%25E4%25BB%2594%25E5%2594%25B1%25E3%2580%258C%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25AD%258C%25E3%2580%258D%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25BC%2595%25E5%258C%2596&d=S%2BP5iCTdX9iTDztVuYOIb3%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=9154f32b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/23468/%E4%BA%BA%E9%8F%88-%E9%A1%98%E6%A6%AE%E5%85%89%E6%AD%B8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E7%9A%87%E4%BB%81%E6%9B%B8%E9%99%A2-23468/qc%E4%BB%94%E5%94%B1%E3%80%8C%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%8C%E3%80%8D%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E5%8C%96</a><br />\n<br />\n眾說<br />\nQC仔唱「香港國歌」年輕化<br />\n撰文: 一悠 | 發佈日期: 12.09.19<br />\n<br />\n請支持《眾新聞》，成為訂戶<br />\n<br />\n今天早上7時45分，路經皇仁書院（香港銅鑼灣），原來QC仔的早操&mdash;&mdash;是唱「香港國歌」（《願榮光歸香港》），人鏈當然是指定動作，加上各界男男女女延至中央圖書館，看都看不完......<br />\n<br />\n最大特點，是這個早操有&mdash;&mdash;「年輕化」的走勢，form1、form2仔，細細粒粒的增加了！（我故意遠些影相）。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭婆婆得把口「重建互信」、「真誠對話」，而家連「form one 仔都郁，你就玩龜縮」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2019/09/%E9%A1%98%E6%A6%AE%E5%85%89%E6%AD%B8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E4%BA%BA%E9%8F%88-%E7%9A%87%E4%BB%81%E6%9B%B8%E9%99%A2-20190912121041_ec2d_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2019%2F09%2F%25E9%25A1%2598%25E6%25A6%25AE%25E5%2585%2589%25E6%25AD%25B8%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%258F%2588-%25E7%259A%2587%25E4%25BB%2581%25E6%259B%25B8%25E9%2599%25A2-20190912121041_ec2d_large.jpg&h=989b9aa4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n人鏈現在是最有力的和平抗爭動作。一悠攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2019/09/%E4%BA%BA%E9%8F%88-%E7%9A%87%E4%BB%81%E6%9B%B8%E9%99%A2-%E9%A1%98%E6%A6%AE%E5%85%89%E6%AD%B8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-20190912120945_2ddf_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2019%2F09%2F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%258F%2588-%25E7%259A%2587%25E4%25BB%2581%25E6%259B%25B8%25E9%2599%25A2-%25E9%25A1%2598%25E6%25A6%25AE%25E5%2585%2589%25E6%25AD%25B8%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-20190912120945_2ddf_large.jpg&h=655bd0db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n皇仁仔人鏈有年輕化趨勢。一悠攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2019/09/%E4%BA%BA%E9%8F%88-%E9%A1%98%E6%A6%AE%E5%85%89%E6%AD%B8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E7%9A%87%E4%BB%81%E6%9B%B8%E9%99%A2-20190912120922_1d79_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2019%2F09%2F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%258F%2588-%25E9%25A1%2598%25E6%25A6%25AE%25E5%2585%2589%25E6%25AD%25B8%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E7%259A%2587%25E4%25BB%2581%25E6%259B%25B8%25E9%2599%25A2-20190912120922_1d79_large.jpg&h=49ee12ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&lrm; 今天皇仁人鏈，中一中二的學生很多。一悠攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2019/09/%E9%A1%98%E6%A6%AE%E5%85%89%E6%AD%B8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E7%9A%87%E4%BB%81%E6%9B%B8%E9%99%A2-%E4%BA%BA%E9%8F%88-20190912121013_1bd9_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2019%2F09%2F%25E9%25A1%2598%25E6%25A6%25AE%25E5%2585%2589%25E6%25AD%25B8%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E7%259A%2587%25E4%25BB%2581%25E6%259B%25B8%25E9%2599%25A2-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%258F%2588-20190912121013_1bd9_large.jpg&h=05df8d67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n人鏈伸延到中央圖書館。一悠攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《願榮光歸香港》歌詞<br />\n<br />\n作詞：t, 眾連登仔<br />\n作曲：thomas dgx yhl<br />\n編曲：t, bp, clk<br />\n<br />\n何以 這土地 淚再流<br />\n何以 令眾人 亦憤恨<br />\n昂首 拒默沉 吶喊聲 響透<br />\n盼自由 歸於 這裡<br />\n<br />\n何以 這恐懼 抹不走<br />\n何以 為信念 從沒退後<br />\n何解 血在流 但邁進聲 響透<br />\n建自由 光輝 香港<br />\n<br />\n在晚星 墜落 徬徨午夜<br />\n迷霧裡 最遠處吹來 號角聲<br />\n捍自由 來齊集這裡 來全力抗對<br />\n勇氣 智慧 也永不滅<br />\n<br />\n黎明來到 要光復 這香港<br />\n同行兒女 為正義 時代革命<br />\n祈求 民主與自由 萬世都不朽<br />\n我願榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請加入成為眾新聞的月費訂戶，長期支持我們的工作。所有訂戶都可以收到我們的「每周時事」通訊 。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n月費訂戶網址：<a href=\"http://hkcnews.com/aboutus/#subscribe\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkcnews.com%2Faboutus%2F%23subscribe&d=S%2BP5iCTdX9iTDztVuYOIb3%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=04c8e23f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hkcnews.com/aboutus/#subscribe</a><br />\n<br />\n博客 | 一悠<br />\n【一悠・到此一遊】喜歡談古論今，也常談股論金。心理、鋼琴、股票、教育，交义感染，交流一下。學歷：香港中文大學文學士，研究院教育文憑，澳洲新南威爾斯大學碩士（堅有證書㗎，卻無野雞大學博士，也不必請律師去找證書）"},{"pid":"b41bca852d7bee84b23c8ffb4223090ce01f28dd","tid":1563862,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:24:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig